item.title: Making a 317 load 474 data help
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

[quote=“swiftclanhype, post:3, topic:546819”][quote author=sk8rdude461 link=topic=665715.msg4450457#msg4450457 date=1410985231]
I don’t get your issue, they all basically tell you where they go.

Animations readValues = Animation.java (Weird how that’s kind of obvious…)
GFX readValues = SpotAnim.java (not as obvious, but it tells you directly in the code)
Item readValues = ItemDef (Again, obvious).
NPC readValues = EntityDef (Obvious to anyone that knows this file is for NPCs.)
[/quote]
im trying to add them to a blank source/client so i dont have all of them[/quote]
You indeed do have all of them. Otherwise the cache wouldn’t load all the data…
You might have a non-renamed client. So they’re all Class1, Class2, Class3, Class4 and so on…
